quote_last: , December 14. In another fifty-eight minutes he would set sail for America. He did not want to leave his bride; he did not want to go.
quote_raw: It was 5:02 a.m., December 14. In another fifty-eight minutes he would set sail for America. He did not want to leave his bride; he did not want to go.
title: The Prize
author: Brenda Joyce
